{"name": "ovos-stt-plugin-server", "metadata": {"name": "ovos-stt-plugin-server", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: Apache Software License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Topic :: Text Processing :: Linguistic"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OpenVoiceOS/ovos-stt-server-plugin", "license": "Apache-2.0", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["ovos-plugin-manager"], "summary": "ovos stt server plugin for mycroft", "upload_time": 1732494621}, "documentation": ["## Description\n\nOpenVoiceOS companion plugin for [OpenVoiceOS STT Server](https://github.com/OpenVoiceOS/ovos-stt-http-server)\n\n## Install\n\n```bash\npip install ovos-stt-plugin-server\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\n```json\n  \"stt\": {\n    \"module\": \"ovos-stt-plugin-server\",\n    \"ovos-stt-plugin-server\": {\n      \"url\": \"https://0.0.0.0:8080/stt\",\n      \"verify_ssl\": true\n    },\n }\n```\n\nfor audio language detection\n\n```json\n  \"listener\": {\n    \"audio_transformers\": {\n        \"ovos-audio-lang-server-plugin\": {\n          \"url\": \"https://0.0.0.0:8080/lang_detect\",\n          \"verify_ssl\": true\n        }\n    }\n  }\n```\n\n### Security warning\n\nPlease note that while you can set `verify_ssl` to `false` to disable SSL\nverification, this is not recommended and should only be used for testing\npurposes. Consider using a private CA or certificates signed using\n[Let's Encrypt](https://letsencrypt.org/) instead.\n\n## Public servers\n\npublic server status page can be found at https://github.com/OpenVoiceOS/status\n\nthe default public servers run [Whisper](https://github.com/OpenVoiceOS/ovos-stt-plugin-fasterwhisper)\n\nWhile there are associated risks with public servers, we value your trust in our products, learn more in Jarbas blog post [The Trust Factor in Public Servers](https://jarbasal.github.io/blog/2023/10/14/the-trust-factor-in-public-servers.html)\n\n\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.version", "documentation": ["START_VERSION_BLOCK"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.version.VERSION_MAJOR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.version.VERSION_MINOR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.version.VERSION_BUILD", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.version.VERSION_ALPHA", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server._whisper_lang", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.engine", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.d", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.jfk", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.ca", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.audio", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.s", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.pred", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.e", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.s", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.pred", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.e", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.OVOSServerLangClassifier", "bases": ["AudioLanguageDetector"], "methods": [{"name": "ovos_stt_plugin_server.OVOSServerLangClassifier.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "config", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns"